    "body": "I'm going to leave it to the user to determine whether it should mine or not. A person is a better judge then a computer program in this case:\n- Miner A wants to mine on the network\n- Malicious miner B starts propagating fake blocks to miner A\n- Miner A receives malicious blocks and waits with mining (Catching up ...)\n- Miner B continues mining on the true chain\n- Miner B gets the moolah\n- Miner A is sad :-(\n",
